29:46.240 --> 29:48.600
with the ideal that certainly, at the beginning of love,

29:48.600 --> 29:50.760
when you're feeling a tense romantic love,

29:50.760 --> 29:53.840
one at least in my own experiences and the experiences

29:53.840 --> 29:55.440
that a lot of people I interviewed for the book

29:55.440 --> 29:57.960
was that you'd meet someone who you liked.

29:57.960 --> 30:03.000
And part of that intensity was sort of inventing an ideal,

30:03.000 --> 30:05.480
oh my god, this person's amazing.

30:05.480 --> 30:08.520
This is the, they do this and that.

30:08.520 --> 30:10.600
And she's funny and all this.

30:10.600 --> 30:13.560
