30:22.160 --> 30:23.800
in the house when she comes in.

30:23.800 --> 30:26.160
You know, whatever your thing is, whatever your little,

30:26.160 --> 30:32.000
and so the ideal starts to, the ideal no longer exists.

30:32.000 --> 30:33.280
The ideal is kind of shattered.

30:33.280 --> 30:36.200
And I think that with online dating,

30:36.200 --> 30:38.200
one of the things online dating allows you to do

30:38.200 --> 30:41.040
is become addicted to that ideal over and over again

30:41.040 --> 30:43.280
because just because you can meet more people.

30:43.280 --> 30:45.200
It's got to, you know, I want to feel that again.

30:45.200 --> 30:46.640
I want to feel that infatuation.

30:46.640 --> 30:49.000
So I met a lot of people who would kind of, you know,

30:49.000 --> 30:51.160
the serial online data that the person who always

30:51.160 --> 30:54.080
was looking for that kind of next early fix.

30:54.080 --> 30:56.160
